agandha","description":"An adaptogen known for helping the body manage stress, Ashwagandha supports calm mood and resilience, helping you feel steady and balanced throughout the day."}},"ingredient_9HRAAA":{"type":"ingredient","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/vera-beverage_Ingredient_Card_L-Theanine.jpg","icon_svg":"","title":"L-Theanine","description":"L-Theanine promotes a state of calm alertness — supporting focus and concentration while helping reduce mental tension and distractions."}},"ingredient_ewPAjU":{"type":"ingredient","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/vera-beverage_New_B12.jpg","icon_svg":"","title":"B-12","description":"Vitamin B-12 helps convert food into\nusable energy and supports brain and\nnervous system function — contributing\nto sustained, everyday energy."}},"ingredient_JbtQQJ":{"type":"ingredient","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/vera-beverage_Ingredient_Card_Magnesium.jpg","icon_svg":"","title":"Magnesium","description":"An essential mineral involved in hundreds of enzymatic reactions, Magnesium supports muscle and nerve function, energy production, and helps maintain a healthy, balanced mood."}}},"block_order":["ingredient_Ewj3hy","ingredient_9PnYYY","ingredient_jLYEfP","ingredient_9HRAAA","ingredient_ewPAjU","ingredient_JbtQQJ"],"name":"Mood Focus Clarity","settings":{"background_color":"#f2f2f2","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":50,"title":"MOOD + FOCUS + CLARITY","title_color":"#8a2d73","title_size_desktop":62,"title_size_tablet":46,"title_size_mobile":38,"subtitle":"What's inside — and why it matters.","subtitle_color":"#555555","subtitle_size_desktop":16,"subtitle_size_mobile":14,"cards_per_row_desktop":4,"cards_per_row_tablet":3,"cards_per_row_mobile":1,"card_gap":20,"card_bg_color":"#ffffff","card_title_color":"#464646","card_title_size_desktop":18,"card_title_size_mobile":16,"card_desc_color":"#464646","card_desc_size_desktop":16,"card_desc_size_mobile":14,"button_text":"FIND OUT MORE","button_u