 of the grape juice, all the other functional\/natural ingredients. Black Cherry is my favorite. Can’t believe it’s only 45 calories."}},"testimonial_wtzrYP":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"rating":5,"reviewer_name":"Morgan – Miami, FL","review_title":"Checks Every Box","review_body":"I am very careful about what I eat and drink. Vera checks all the boxes for me. All natural and healthy ingredients and not too much sugar. It is my go-to drink at home and at work. I’m hooked!"}},"testimonial_PXQfwk":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"rating":5,"reviewer_name":"Alexandria – Santa Monica, CA","review_title":"My Social Go-To","review_body":"I gave up alcohol over a year ago and it really changed my life. The biggest challenge was finding that right beverage for social situations. Vera truly lifts my mood and it so delicious."}},"testimonial_LKbjCB":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"rating":5,"reviewer_name":"Max – Scottsdale, AZ","review_title":"Golf Game Upgrade","review_body":"I have been smuggling Vera onto the golf course and have begged my club to start carrying it. Vera is delicious and it makes me feel clear headed and calm. I would dare to say it has shaved a few strokes off my game! The Raspberry kicks A$$!"}},"testimonial_QpmcAM":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"rating":5,"reviewer_name":"Casey – NY, NY","review_title":"Energy, No Jitters","review_body":"Love, love, love! I have given up coffee and soda at work and switched to Vera. It gives me energy to get through the day but without the jitters. It is also delicious and healthy. Blueberry-Mint is my fav."}},"testimonial_6YLaN7":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"rating":5,"reviewer_name":"Jake – Columbus, OH","review_title":"Post-Gym Ritual","review_body":"This stuff rocks! I am very health conscious and feel good about drinking Vera. I always enjoy a can after the gym and have recently started drinking it when hanging with friends instead of drinking cocktails or beer."}},"testimonial_YHbLmj":{"type"